## Architecture Summary

```
                     ┌──────────────────────┐
                     │      USER QUERY      │
                     └──────────┬───────────┘
                                │
                     ┌──────────▼───────────┐
                     │ 🧠 MARKETING-ORCHESTRATOR  │  ← HUB
                     │  (INTENT CLASSIFIER) │
                     └────┬─────┬─────┬─────┘
                          │     │     │
              ┌───────────┘┐    │    ┌┴──────────┐
              ▼            ▼    ▼    ▼            ▼
         🔍 SEO     ✍️ Content  📱 Social  📊 Analytics  📧 Email
         Researcher  Writer    Manager   Reporter     Campaign Mgr
              │         │         │         │            │
              └─────────┴─────────┴─────────┴────────────┘
                                │
                     ┌──────────▼───────────┐
                     │  SYNTHESIZED PLAN    │
                     └──────────────────────┘
```

**Key architectural property:** The orchestrator analyzes each query, classifies intent into 1+ categories (seo, content, social, analytics, email), and **dynamically dispatches** only the relevant specialists — in parallel or sequentially, as it decides. No fixed pipeline, no mandatory order. Each specialist is an independent spoke.
